snippet.title: NASCAR Grand National Series Expansion Pack (1997) Trailer
snippet.description:
Addon car and track pack for NASCAR Racing 2 (1996).

Somewhat amusing this trailer is cut from a video that was on the CD of the addon being advertised... Which you'd already bought by the time you saw it. You can donate to RSC for whatever reason here:
https://racesimcentral.net/donate/
